aa(lp112
VReally, no heroic deed \u2014
p113
aVwe simply need to be close.
p114
aVAnd if we are afraid of something
p115
aVor we don't understand something,
p116
aVwe need to ask.
p117
aa(lp118
VLet's be curious
p119
aVbut never indifferent.
p120
aVLet's have the courage to look each other in the eye,
p121
aVbecause by looking,
p122
aVwe can open a whole world to someone else.
